<FIRST>a e BC-WKD--TurntableTips 1stADD   09-07 0309</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-WKD--Turntable Tips, 1st ADD,0353</SECOND>
<HEAD>$Adv08</HEAD>
<HEAD>For release Friday, Sept. 8, and thereafter</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 COUNTRY SINGLES
</TEXT>
