orld after <LOCATION> Japan </LOCATION>. It imported $ 2.3 billion worth of <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> farm products last year. <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> ran a trade deficit of $ 8.5 billion with <LOCATION> South </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Korea </LOCATION> last year.
